Mfsadd
  Function to move MFS partition from one drive to another
  Ability to add existing partitions into MFS set
  Ability to expand MFS set to fill a drive, creating partitions as needed
Restore
  Ability to save extra partitions at end of drive
  Ability to create new MFS partitions to fill drive
MfsCopy
  New tool to do a direct drive to drive copy of MFS.
